## Concrete Numbers Example

```
Scenario: 1000 virtual threads, each does:
  - 1ms CPU work
  - 999ms blocking (API call)
  - 1ms CPU work

Platform Threads (8 OS threads):
  1000 tasks / 8 threads = 125 rounds
  Each round: 1001ms
  Total: ~125 seconds ❌

Virtual Threads (8 carrier threads):
  All 1000 start almost simultaneously
  Each carrier handles ~125 VTs
  During 999ms block → carrier runs other VTs
  Total: ~1001ms ✅ (just one API call duration!)
```

