## The Waiter Analogy — More Precisely

```
Platform Thread Waiter:
  Takes order → stands at table → food arrives → serves → moves to next table
  1 waiter stuck per table the whole time

Virtual Thread Waiter:
  Takes order → goes to kitchen window (blocked/parked)
  While waiting → takes order from table 2 → goes to kitchen window
  While waiting → takes order from table 3 → goes to kitchen window
  Kitchen signals table 1 ready → serves table 1
  Kitchen signals table 2 ready → serves table 2

1 waiter body (carrier) serving N tables (virtual threads)
The waiter's LEGS (carrier) never stop moving!
```

